icer on march   had previously served as our president and chief operating officer since january  and has served as one of our directors since october  prior to joining brightcove mr mendels served as senior vice president and general manager at adobe systems incorporated a software company from december  to august  mr mendels had no full time employment between leaving adobe in august  and joining our board in october  he joined adobe when it acquired macromedia inc where he was a member of the executive team and executive vice president and general manager mr mendels joined macromedia in  and served in many roles including leading japan sales and establishing macromedia kk leading worldwide marketing and as general manager of macromedias web publishing business unit mr mendels holds a ba in east asian studies from wesleyan university and an ma in japanese from the university of california at berkeley mr mendels was selected to serve on our board due to the perspective and experience he brings as our chief executive officer and his extensive background in the internet and software industries source brightcove inc on    sign up for equilar atlas and view david r mendelss full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like david r mendels more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in david r mendelss network and community follow changes in david r mendelss employment and moneyinmotion connect with david r mendels through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example david r mendels david r mendelss connections  sign up now to view david r mendelss  connections » matthew a thompson executive vice president worldwide field operations adobe charles m geschke board member adobe james e daley lead director adobe andrew w feinberg president and chief operating officer brightcove inc paul f goetz former senior vice president worldw